Class MethodAnalyzer

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpf.ListenerAdapter
      • gov.nasa.jpf.listener.MethodAnalyzer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JPFListener, PublisherExtension, SearchListener, VMListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OverlappingMethodAnalyzer

    public class MethodAnalyzer
extends ListenerAdapter
    analyzes call/execute sequences of methods closely modeled after the DeadlockAnalyzer, i.e. keeps it's own log and doesn't require full instruction trace <2do> this needs to be refactored with DeadlockAnalyzer - the whole trace mgnt (except of the printing) can be made generic
